Class StandardMXBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.management.StandardMBean
      • com.camerontec.util.jmx.mxbean.StandardMXBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DynamicMBean, MBeanRegistration

    public class StandardMXBean
extends StandardMBean
    Wraps an MXBean into a StandardMBean which uses annotations to determine descriptions and operation parameter names.
